Package com.wesleyware.daowiz

An abstraction of a SQL database into objects

See:
          Description

Class Summary
Constraints This is an immutable object representaion of DB constraints.
Field This is an immutable object representaion of a DB field.
Record This is an object representation of a single DB record.
RecordDao This is a generic DAO that will be inherited by each table specific DAO to contain custom code.
 

Exception Summary
InvalidPkException Exception to be thrown when parameters used in record constructor are invalid.
